InsightLens — Auto-Generate Stories from Dashboards with One Click

Summary:
Dashboards are rich in data but often require manual effort to interpret and explain — especially for non-technical audiences. 
InsightLens is a GenAI-powered solution that transforms complex KPIs and visuals into clear, natural-language narratives in seconds.

With a single click, users receive bullet-point summaries or detailed reports highlighting key trends, anomalies, and business insights. 
Designed to work seamlessly with existing BI tools, this idea reduces interpretation time and empowers faster, more informed decision-making.

Alternative Title:
DataSpeaks — Let Your Dashboard Tell the Story
SummarAI — Your AI-Powered Dashboard Narrator
ReadMyDash — Instant Narratives from Complex Charts
